General.Name: Macerich Company
General.Description: We own 43 million square feet of real estate consisting primarily of interests in 40 regional retail centers that serve as community cornerstones. As a leading owner, operator and developer of high-quality retail real estate in densely populated and attractive U.S. markets, our portfolio is concentrated in California, the Pacific Northwest, Phoenix/Scottsdale, and the Metro New York to Washington, D.C. corridor. We are firmly dedicated to advancing environmental goals, social good and sound corporate governance. As a recognized leader in sustainability, The Macerich Company (the "Company") has achieved a #1 GRESB ranking for the North American retail sector for ten consecutive years.
